00:08:05.510 --> 00:08:07.170
Remember to go to class later.

00:08:09.300 --> 00:08:11.100
Your handwriting is quite nice.

00:08:22.810 --> 00:08:23.910
Midterm exam?

00:08:24.510 --> 00:08:27.370
