Guan Riqing and Zefang.

00:17:37.070 --> 00:17:37.930
Zefang?

00:17:39.400 --> 00:17:41.100
Guan Riqing and me,

00:17:41.440 --> 00:17:42.300
me.

00:17:46.390 --> 00:17:48.120
